{"article_id":"vKpfzb2Td0f4SNQ3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Justice Department on Thursday sent Congress copies of the memos","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that former FBI Director James B. Comey wrote on his interactions with President Trump ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"moving to head off a looming subpoena from Capitol Hill .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"The memos show Mr. Trump , during a private dinner with Mr. Comey , complaining about his then-National Security Adviser Michael Flynn ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"\" the guy has serious judgment issues . \"","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Trump also asked Mr. Comey for his loyalty","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"he wanted the Russia investigation brought to an end ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"the memos show .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Mr. Trump told him","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"\" he needed loyalty","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and expected loyalty , \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Comey recalled .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Mr. Comey said","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"he \" did not reply or even nod or change my facial expression ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"which","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"[ Mr. Trump ] noted","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"because we came back to it later . \"","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Trump also disputed the salacious information","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"contained in the so-called \" Steele Dossier , \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"compiled on behalf of the Clinton campaign and the Democratic National Committee .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"\" There were no prostitutes .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"There were never prostitutes , \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Mr. Trump said in response to one of the dossier ' s accusations .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":3},{"id":26,"text":"Comey appears aware of McCabe conflict in newly released memos","depth":3},{"id":27,"text":"All told , 15 pages were sent to Congress","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"- and then quickly leaked online .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Of the 15 pages , 10 contain classified or secret information","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that has been redacted ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"either because they reveal intelligence information or foreign relations information .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Copies of redacted versions of the memos were sent to multiple House and Senate committees .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Unredacted versions with the classified information included","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"will be sent Friday by secure means ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Mr. Boyd said .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Mr. Comey testified to Congress last year","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that he specifically avoided classified information in some of the memos","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"so the content could be used .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" My thinking was","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"if I write in such a way","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that won ' t include anything","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that trigger classification ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that will make it easier to discuss within FBI and government , \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"he said then .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"But that only applied to some of the seven memos .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"On one of them , Mr. Comey himself wrote a note","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"he was marking it at the \" Secret \" classification level","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"because of the information .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Some of Mr. Comey ' s critics have said","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"he could face legal troubles over the memos ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"since he leaked some of them to a professor friend","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"who then leaked contents to The New York Times .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Rep. Elijah Cummings , the ranking Democrat on the House Oversight Committee ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"who was one of those","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"who received the memos Thursday ,","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"the documents could clear Mr. Comey .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"a key memo","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"that Mr. Comey ' s friend shared with The New York Times ,","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"which was released as part of the batch ,","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"\" is clearly marked ' UNCLASSIFIED . ' \"","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"But Sen. Chuck Grassley , Iowa Republican and chairman of the Senate Judiciary Committee , gave a different version of events earlier this year .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"Mr. Comey wrote seven memos ,","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"four of them were classified ,","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"and four were given to the friend .","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"That ,","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"Mr. Grassley said ,","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"means \" at least one \" of the memos","depth":16},{"id":72,"text":"the former director gave to his friend","depth":16},{"id":73,"text":"was classified .","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"Two of the four classified memos are labeled at the \" Secret \" level","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"and two are labeled \" Confidential . \"","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"Reps. Bob Goodlatte , Devin Nunes and Trey Gowdy","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"- committee chairmen","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"who prompted the memos ' release -","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"they exposed Mr. Comey as a partisan brawler .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Mr. Comey never wrote in the memos","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that he felt hindered in his work ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"they said .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" While former Director Comey went to great lengths","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to set dining room scenes ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"discuss height requirements ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"describe the multiple times","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"he felt complimented ,","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"and myriad other extraneous facts ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"he never once mentioned the most relevant fact of all ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"which was whether he felt obstructed in his investigation , \"","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"the chairmen said in a joint statement .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"They also said","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"it was \" significant \" that Mr. Comey immediately began tracking his conversations with Mr. Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"but never took that step with his then-Deputy Director Andrew McCabe or Attorney General Loretta E. Lynch ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"about whom he had expressed concerns as politically tainted .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"They also said","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Mr. Comey ' s \" animus \" toward the president is laid bare .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"\" He was willing to work for someone","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"he deemed morally unsuited for office ,","depth":16},{"id":101,"text":"capable of lying ,","depth":17},{"id":102,"text":"requiring of personal loyalty ,","depth":18},{"id":103,"text":"worthy of impeachment ,","depth":19},{"id":104,"text":"and sharing the traits of a mob boss .","depth":19},{"id":105,"text":"Former Director Comey was willing to overlook all of the aforementioned characteristics","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"in order to keep his job .","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"In his eyes , the real crime was his own firing , \"","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"the three Republicans concluded .","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"But Mr. Cumming said Thursday night","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that the memos back up what Mr. Comey has said -","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"that the president wanted the Russia investigation to end ,","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"and that he wanted Mr. Comey ' s loyalty .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"\" President Trump ' s interference was a blatant effort","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"to deny justice ,","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"and Director Comey was right to document it","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"as it happened","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"- in real time , \"","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"Mr. Cummings said .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Congress had asked for the memos earlier this week","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"but Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein said","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"more time was needed for the redactions .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Mr. Comey said","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"he wrote the memos","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"because he was concerned about his interactions with Mr. Trump","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"and wanted contemporaneous records .","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"After he was fired last May ,","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"he gave those memos to a friend","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"who works as a law professor at Columbia University .","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"The friend leaked the memos to The New York Times ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"which were the basis for a story on the difficult relationship between Mr. Comey and the president .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"Appearing on CNN on Thursday afternoon ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"Mr. Comey said","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"he was \" OK \" with the memos being released .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"The memos are viewed as an important part of special counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation into Russian collusion with the Trump campaign .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Mr. Mueller is looking into","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"whether Mr. Comey ' s firing was an attempt","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"to undermine an investigation into Russian meddling .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"The memos were released","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"to head off a looming subpoena from Mr. Goodlatte , chairman of the House Judiciary Committee .","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Also this week , a group of conservative lawyers asked the Justice Department to bring charges against Mr. Comey along with other Obama administration officials","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"who were part of the investigation into former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton ' s emails .","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"The Justice Department handed over the Comey memos faster than other recent Congressional document requests .","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"Last week , it handed over document","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"related to the Clinton email investigation","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"to the House Intelligence Committee","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"after Rep. Devin Nunes , California Republican , threatened to impeach Mr. Rosenstein and FBI Director Christopher A. Wray over the delay .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"The Justice Department said","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"it was slow to comply","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"because of the volume of documents and number of reductions","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"needed .","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"The Judiciary panel is still awaiting nearly 1.2 million documents from the Justice Department","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"relating to the FBI ' s decision","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"not to charge Mrs. Clinton in the email probe","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"and the application","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"to spy on Trump campaign aide Carter Page under the Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":311,"left":180,"right":310,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":180,"left":158,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":157,"right":2,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":160,"right":178,"